    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breecell is a puzzle game that combines simple mechanics with deep strategy. Enjoy adorable illustrations and a variety of background music while aiming for high scores by clearing cells!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🟥 🟧 🟩 🟦 ⬛️ 🟥 🟧 🟩 🟦 ⬛️ 🟥 🟧 🟩 🟦 ⬛️ 🟥 🟧 🟩 🟦 ⬛️ 🟥 🟧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Basic Rules</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click a cell to make it spread in the directions it's assigned.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/5f1f9d2339f24e7a2488a768f02b6ca0.avif?t=1730643681\" width=300 height=137 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/af776268acf02ce2a37a95dfe6dd7ee8.avif?t=1730643681\" width=300 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Align cells into a square to clear them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/3096d14c86102d267886fc4117efae16.avif?t=1730643681\" width=150 height=137 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chain Combos for High Scores</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more cells you clear at once, the higher your score. Chain combos to aim for even greater points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/29a7c31a2cc2119445fee13ddef70286.poster.avif?t=1730643681\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/29a7c31a2cc2119445fee13ddef70286.webm?t=1730643681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/29a7c31a2cc2119445fee13ddef70286.mp4?t=1730643681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Thrilling Difficulty</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the game progresses, the speed increases, and garbage cells appear!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/29382612d2786c7b3cd47116f928e0cc.poster.avif?t=1730643681\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/29382612d2786c7b3cd47116f928e0cc.webm?t=1730643681\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/29382612d2786c7b3cd47116f928e0cc.mp4?t=1730643681\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Global Rankings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete with players around the world for the top score!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/7c79b9fd3934a188e405b8300d021808.avif?t=1730643681\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras_big/7c79b9fd3934a188e405b8300d021808.avif?t=1730643681 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Genkai Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself with &quot;Genkai Mode,&quot; where the game becomes even harder in a more confined space. Test your limits!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras/f4eee687c336bc2d4132936460b29049.avif?t=1730643681\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271020/extras_big/f4eee687c336bc2d4132936460b29049.avif?t=1730643681 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download now and enjoy a simple yet profound puzzle experience!</p>",
